Package org.cripac.isee.vpe.alg

This package contains applications running vision algorithms.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PedestrianAttrRecogApp
    The PedestrianAttrRecogApp class is a Spark Streaming application which performs pedestrian attribute recognition.
    PedestrianAttrRecogApp.RecogStream  
    PedestrianAttrRecogAppTest
    This is a JUnit test for the DataManagingApp.
    PedestrianReIDUsingAttrApp
    The PedestrianReIDApp class is a Spark Streaming application which performs pedestrian re-identification with attributes.
    PedestrianReIDUsingAttrApp.ReIDStream  
    PedestrianTrackingApp
    The PedestrianTrackingApp class takes in video URLs from Kafka, then process the videos with pedestrian tracking algorithms, and finally push the tracking results back to Kafka.
    PedestrianTrackingApp.RTVideoStreamTrackingStream
    The RTVideoStreamTrackingStream receives web-camera IPs and perform pedestrian tracking on real-time video bit stream from these cameras.
    PedestrianTrackingApp.VideoFragmentTrackingStream  
    PedestrianTrackingApp.VideoFragmentTrackingStream.VideoFragment
